@groundsandhounds is the coffee brand with a purpose. ☕️😇 With every purchase, 20% of the company’s profit goes straight towards supporting rescue initiatives and organizations providing a second chance for pups in need of a helping hand. 🐶🙏How stinkin’ awesome is that?!! 🤍 They have the yummiest coffee in tons of seasonal and classic flavors. My mom’s favorite is the glazed 🍩. AND they have all sorts of adorable apparel, dog toys and more! As you can clearly see in this picture, I can’t get enough!! 😋

Living my BEST LIFE in my new Prancer bed from @shoplovedua ✨It’s big and cozy and makes me feel like the king that I am 👑. Now if only momma could stop taking videos of me so I can go back to my afternoon nap 🥱💤🛌😴
